{
  "texts": [
    "In the future, the integration of AIGC and IVAs will yield an even more intelligent and convenient interactive experience.",
    "Intelligent traffic accident analysis utilizes data analysis and AI for the real-time identification, responsibility determination, accident pattern recognition, and formulation of preventive measures related to traffic accidents (Zheng et al., 2023).",
    "As urbanization and the number of vehicles increase, the road traffic system becomes increasingly complex.",
    "Therefore, it is crucial to achieve precise identification and analysis of traffic accidents, as well as to determine responsibility.",
    "The advantages of AIGC in intelligent traffic accident analysis include its ability to automatically generate and analyze large amounts of data."
  ]
}